                </div>
                <div class="projects__row-content">
                    <h3 class="projects__row-content-title">Managefy</h3>
                    <p class="projects__row-content-desc">
                        Managefy is a web-based business management platform for quotations, invoices, sale orders, purchase orders, reporting, and ZIMRA fiscalisation. It also includes a secure REST API and mobile app support for quick receipt workflows.
                    </p>
                    <a class='btn btn--med btn--theme dynamicBgClr' href='project-9'>Case Study</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="projects__row">
                <div class="projects__row-img-cont">
                    <img src="assets/png/assethome.png"
