                         class="projects__row-img"
                         loading="lazy" />
                </div>
                <div class="projects__row-content">
                    <h3 class="projects__row-content-title">Asset Management System</h3>
                    <p class="projects__row-content-desc">
                        Introducing an innovative web-based Asset Management System designed to streamline your organization's asset tracking and management processes. 
                        This system offers a comprehensive solution to effectively manage your valuable assets such as recording asset information, take inventories, assigning assets to users on short term and long term, asset lending, reporting , calculate asset depreciation and many other functionalities.
                    </p>
                    <a class='btn btn--med btn--theme dynamicBgClr' href='project-1'>Case Study</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="projects__row">
                <div class="projects__row-img-cont">
